schafts- und Technikgeschichte ausgezeichnet.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 4aGeschichte des 20. Jahrhunderts. 4aGeschichtswissenschaft. 4aLeben. 4aMedizin. 4aMedizingeschichte. 4aNeuroleptika. 4aPatientengeschichte. 4aPharmazie. 4aPharmaziegeschichte. 4aPsychiatriegeschichte. 4aScience Studies. 4aWissenschaft. 4aWissenschaftsgeschichte. 7aHISTORY / Modern / 20th Century.2bisacsh  aHistory of Medicine.  aHistory of the 20th Century.  aHistory.  aLife.  aMedicine.  aPharmacy.  aScience.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Complete Package 2010-2013z9783110352856oZDB-23-TSO08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Geschichte 2010-2013z978311037073740uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/transcript.9783839414521zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839414521423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839414521/original  a978-3-11-037073-7  transcript Highlight Collection Geschichte 2010-2013c2010d2013  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-TSOc2010d2013